This month we <a href=\"http:\/\/www.lovedrop.us\/\">start all over again<\/a> and circle around 2 beautiful kids with severe autism.<\/strong> Our goal is to raise $13,000 so we can get them a highly trained service dog. And if possible, three iPads so the family can communicate better with each other (Alex can only speak through technology, and these iPads can do wonders for everyone).\u00a0 It&#8217;s a long shot, but we&#8217;re gonna do our best and see what happens.  If you&#8217;d like to join us, you can become a member of Love Drop <a href=\"http:\/\/www.lovedrop.us\/get-involved\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>I have about a billion other things I wanna say right now, but I think I&#8217;ll leave it at that. I&#8217;m in one of those weird places at the moment where I&#8217;m pondering the meaning of life. I&#8217;m afraid what else I&#8217;ll divulge if I keep on going ;)<\/p>\n<p>God bless, everyone.\u00a0 I love you all more than you know.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>So I thought long and hard about this one, and figured if there were ever a time for me to make an appearance, it&#8217;s now&#8230;. <\/p>\n<p class=\"more\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/this-is-what-micro-giving-can-do\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":43124,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[62,166,90,5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6111","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-charity","category-get-motivated","category-inspiration","category-life"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v24.6 (Yoast SEO v24.5) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>This is What Micro-Giving Can Do | Budgets Are Sexy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-previe